>\n<br />\n前往途中請往紅磡紅隧<br />\n<br />\n龍頭到左紅磡紅隧<br />\n暫時睇油麻地至尖東至理工<br />\n三角形都有人<br />\n請開google map睇地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xknev2A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxknev2A.png&h=e6682edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請不要進入紅磡內</span><br />\n<br />\n回家路線<br />\n何文田<br />\n土瓜灣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請無視紅隧免費放車走言論<br />\n收費站有cam可以捉司機走數<br />\n別戇鳩<br />\n水炮車未出不要叫散紅隧<br />\n可以塞到銅鑼灣</span></span>"},{"pid":"138e93cbff012008a56cd717ab73ce7ed490bfee","tid":1399951,"uid":281430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"你都傻傻， 紅隧道是捉住政府過春袋"},{"pid":"77104ea22ebd507c7505993b5b41a5ac6ab150df","tid":1399951,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be83959ddec9b562013db2fa6089cd115078fb03","tid":1399951,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1d8a7893c5db1eb2681978ff7d79737528c3489a","tid":1399951,"uid":75870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"咁免費10日咪2400萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"我驚一個鐘就比阿狗清左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我車住千幾萬貨 塞停左delay <br />\n比人claim期冇保險<br />\n商家出唔出聲"},{"pid":"02e5a2e9644eae00d35df3f4d45e4e142bd285c7","tid":1399951,"uid":7855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77104ea22ebd507c7505993b5b41a5ac6ab150df","tid":1399951,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be83959ddec9b562013db2fa6089cd115078fb03","tid":1399951,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1d8a7893c5db1eb2681978ff7d79737528c3489a","tid":1399951,"uid":75870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"咁免費10日咪2400萬<img src=